            "detailed_description": "<strong>2015 IGF Winner: Excellence in Audio</strong><br><br>Ephemerid is a rock fairy tale about a paper mayfly.<br><br>Lean back, relax and enjoy it as a whole, as you would a favorite album. Ephemerid is part rhythm game, part point-and-click adventure, and part rock opera.<br><br>KEY FEATURES<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Ephemerid’s beating heart is its original soundtrack, rock guitar with a classical flair.<br></li><li>The world of Ephemerid is faithfully handcrafted out of cut paper, glass, and paint.<br></li><li>Each setting introduces intuitive challenges which play in harmony with the music.</li></ul><br>ACCOLADES<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2015 IGF Winner: Excellence in Audio<br></li><li>2014 SXSW Gamer's Voice Finalist<br></li><li>2014 BIG Festival Finalist<br></li><li>2013 IndieCade Finalist<br></li><li>2013 Captivate Finalist</li></ul>",
